data.description: Owner relocating! Over 1850 sqft of living space. 2020 built home. Better than new, upgraded granite tops, luxury vinyl planking with 4 generous bedrooms, updated modern split floor plan, recently screened lanai, massive fenced backyard recently finished over 10K to in fencing.  Oversized laundry room. Pantry in kitchen. Luxury master bath. Dont miss the abundance of closets! Convenient location, near great schools. Make appointment today to see.
